  <summary date="2023-11-14T20:48:05Z" status="Introduced in House">Justice for Exploited Children Act of 2023

This bill replaces the current maximum civil penalty of $11,000 for a violation of the child labor laws with a minimum civil penalty of $5,000 and a maximum of $132,270 (or, in the case of a violation that causes death or serious injury, $25,000 and $601,150, respectively).</summary>
